PLAYER HELP
COMMUNICATION
You have many options for communication:

 ~CCOMsay~CHLP: Send a message to everyone in the room.
 ~CCOMtell~CHLP: Send a private message to one player, wherever they are.
 ~CCOMchat~CHLP: Send a message to everyone on the 'chat' ~CCOMchannel~CHLP.
 ~CCOMsouls~CHLP: Do a social action.

See also: ~CREFsay, tell, chat, souls
